---
title: Portabello Mushrooms & Prosciutto with Sourdough & Lemony Spinach | Serves 2
description: This is a perfect dish to kick off your weekend and satisfy your savoury cravings. Serve up a café-style brunch in 30 minutes with
herby butter mushrooms, golden prosciutto, fried egg and lemony spinach all on top of crunchy sourdough.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
